Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:26.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:31.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:31.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:37.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:37.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:45.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:45.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:47.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:47.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:53.27,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:53.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:58.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:00:58.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:01:04.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:04.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:09.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:09.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:11.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:15.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:15.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:20.47,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:20.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:26.03,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:26.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:31.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:31.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:36.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:36.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:42.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:42.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:47.37,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:47.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:55.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:55.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:57.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:01.09,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:01.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:06.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:06.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:11.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:11.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:17.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:17.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:25.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:03:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After losing his brother Ace during \Nthe War of the Best against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was consumed with unbearable sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is, however, an untold \Nstory of the brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...10 years ago in the East \NBlue - Luffy and Ace as boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Take Good Care of Him! A \NLetter from the Brother!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace is not dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy, I know. I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too risky to go to Gray Terminal now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you're wounded and \Nthere are troops everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But...!\N--It was a big fire! And chances are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...slim but we all want to believe \Nthat the boss and Ace are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dogra went there to look for \Nthem now so trust him and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's having a hard \Ntime - not just you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The fishing boat has been hit!\N--How's the child?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made the Celestial Dragon mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! The ship is catching fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did they shoot me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saint Jalmack! There is a child on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When someone flies a black flag, he's \Na pirate regardless of who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But most importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:05:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A commoner shouldn't cross \Nthe path of my ship!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What was that ship doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an important ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't \Nwanna put the Celestial Dragon in a bad mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move the shipwreck already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey guys, those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace... Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's severely wounded! \NHurry up and treat her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think that I was dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But...!\N--Why are you crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not dead, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:07:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is just happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you about the night of the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we left with Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what happened to you and boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We fought against Bluejam...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we barely defeated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we tried to follow you guys right away
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the fire was blocking our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! There's no way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait!\N--What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:08:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice since I told them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I'd take responsibility \Nfor bringing you home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow my lead. Don't get \Nseparated at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dadan! Are you alright, Dadan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it through the fire
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbut Dadan got severely burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to get to the riverside \Nin the In-Between Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me! You can't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the town to steal some \Nmedicine and get something to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:09:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and tried to save Dadan's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry \Nabout me so just go, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap! I thought you were \Nresponsible for bringing me home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some survivors could be around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let anyone get away! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay, we see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, \NI'm glad that you both survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry that I made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe what \Nhappened to Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Sabo is worrying about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Banzai!\N--Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another rude commoner could \Nappear at any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Watch carefully.\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how's Sabo doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad that Ace is back \Nand Dadan is recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, at that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help getting fired up sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always afraid that if I run,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave something important behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know but I think that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when he faced a cloud \Nof enemies beyond his power,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger would never run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he suicidal? Running \Naway is a strategy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right but he'd never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he'd leave the \Npeople he loved behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he ran, he would put his crew in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, "he wouldn't run \Naway" isn't quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't let the enemy have \Na chance to go after his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd change into a sort of \Ndemon in those situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He once destroyed a country's entire military
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because they talked badly about his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd become violent when angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NHe was short-tempered and selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was naive and straightforward \Nlike a child at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because his early life was like Ace's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hated to lose those he loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was that reckless but he survived,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and became the King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he got a bad reputation, \Nhis crew trusted him implicitly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I as a Navy soldier \Ncouldn't help respecting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I decided to take care of Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:12:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones taking care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Have something you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people of the world still hate Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And while Ace hates his father,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it really is "like father, like son."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's see which \None of you will win...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dogra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking for Ace and Dadan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?! Sabo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop lying, you fool! \NDon't even joke about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying or joking \Nabout it! It was so sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could barely believe what I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Sabo went back to his family's home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could he be at sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! He went home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hoodlum like me can \Nunderstand how he feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People don't always wanna \Ngo back to their home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he was really happy, \Nhe wouldn't go out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't go out to sea by himself \Nwith a black flag on his ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was all by myself even if I had parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why didn't we go \Nthere to take him back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the guy who killed \NSabo now?! I'm gonna kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kill the Celestial Dragon?! \NThat's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.90,0:13:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so confident even \Nthough you're not that strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do?! They'll just kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die and people will \Nforget you by tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a nameless kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo was killed by this country! This world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father changed the world by his death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you become a man that important,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you can do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tie this fool up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Stop crying like a girl, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you come to your senses, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Untie him.\N--Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where's Luffy?\N--He's been crying all night and he's sleeping now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! You're not gonna believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a letter from Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:41.95,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,TO MY BROTHERS AT MT. CORVO FROM SABO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've sent it before he went out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna go to the town! \NIt's for us, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ace, Luffy, I hope you guys \Nweren't hurt in the fire."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm worrying about you both but \NI believe that you're okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry to say it, guys, but when you \Nget this letter, I'll already be..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...out on the sea."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Things led to things and I decided \Nto set out to sea before you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My destination will be anywhere but here."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm gonna become stronger \Nand become a pirate!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The three of us have to become \Nthe freest pirates ever."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"One day, let's meet up again somewhere."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Somewhere on the wide open sea! \NDefinitely, someday!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"By the way, Ace, which of us \Ndo you think is the bigger brother?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:17:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Two big brothers and one little brother."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's odd but our brotherhood \Nis my treasure."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy is still a weak crybaby but..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...he is our little brother \Nso take good care of him!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could they call themselves \Nobservers?! They're partying everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't covered Sabo's story...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that his parents didn't take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His parents are nobles
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're powerless against the World \NGovernment and Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Luffy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He still isn't eating much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he still eats twice as much as we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Sabo's death really got to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta set out to sea someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of this \Ncountry and live freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:19:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer are you gonna lie there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The treasure that we were hiding \Nin the forest is all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The survivors from Bluejam's crew took \Nit or maybe the military found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't care about the treasure anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the pirate savings that \NI was gonna share with Sabo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Sabo didn't need it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll just let it go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use having treasure \Nif you can't even protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ace... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More, and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More and more, more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More, more and more, more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More and more, more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna become even stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can protect anything or anyone! \NI don't have to lose anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, please don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! Worry about yourself first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're far weaker than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo told me to take care of you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise that I'll never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I leave a wimpy \Nbrother like you behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh... Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not smart so I don't quite \Nknow what really killed Sabo yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it must be something opposed to freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo died before he knew freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We exchanged that same cup \Nof sake and we're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So listen, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to live without leaving any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys from noble family...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will become full nobles when they turn 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I need to leave here by 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta go out to sea someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and live as we like. \NFreer than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.19,0:22:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.01,0:22:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we'll make enemies of many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the old man will become our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.23,0:22:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta risk everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.47,0:22:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go out to sea at 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we will become... pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Ace are stricken with grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.09,0:23:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they hold on to their \Ndream of becoming pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set off toward the future again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their day of departure will come...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.47,0:23:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To achieve the dream that \NSabo was unable to realize!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To Live Up to the Promise! \NDepartures of Their Own!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
